videos.description: Chris Johnson dialed up the jump pass to Devin Chafin for the first touchdown in overtime against TCU.
videos.headline: Baylor scores with jump pass in overtime

videos.description: A pass interference penalty is called, leading TCU to set up a first-and-goal in overtime. Trevone Boykin scores two plays later to tie it up with No. 7 Baylor and force a second OT.
videos.headline: Pass interference sets up tying TCU score

videos.headline: T. Boykin run for 1 yd for a TD

videos.description: Trevone Boykin found KaVontae Turpin in the back of the end zone to give TCU a 28-21 lead against Baylor in double overtime.
videos.headline: Boykin throws go-ahead TD in double OT

videos.description: On fourth down, Baylor RB Devin Chafin is stopped by two TCU defenders without gaining any yards, giving TCU the win in double overtime.
videos.headline: TCU's fourth-down stop in double OT wins game

videos.description: Check out highlights from TCU's 28-21 double-overtime win over Baylor.
videos.headline: TCU's victory in 15 seconds
